data.description: SELLER ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS! AN EASY SHOW! Welcome to your dream Florida oasis! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a 2-car garage is the epitome of coastal living. With its open floor plan and a split bedroom layout, this residence offers both comfort and privacy for you and your loved ones.   As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the tasteful tile flooring that runs throughout the home, providing a cool and elegant touch to the space. The neutral décor and modern updates, including sliding doors and charming shiplap wall decor, make this home feel fresh and inviting.  One of the true highlights of this property is the incredible outdoor space, designed for those who appreciate the Florida lifestyle. Imagine yourself relaxing by the shimmering pool, enjoying the warm sunshine, or unwinding in the covered seating area, complete with a cozy fire pit for those cool evenings. The oversized lanai cage ensures you can enjoy the outdoors without any unwanted guests.  This prime location offers proximity to a wide array of restaurants, shopping destinations, and other amenities, ensuring you have everything you need just moments away. And for those who love the beach, you're in luck - Siesta Key and other beautiful beaches are only minutes away, allowing you to embrace the coastal life to the fullest.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this magnificent property your own. It's time to live the Florida dream – schedule a showing today and start your journey to coastal living at its finest!  All measurements approximate and to be independently verified by Buyer. Pending Release.
